.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, rose, balloon-flower
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the japanese is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Flower         | bellflower      | balloon-flower | zinnia      | rose |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

