.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
City: boston, prague, venice, miami
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
7. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| City    | venice   | miami      | prague       | boston |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, september, january, july
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday      | january   | july          | september | february        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

