.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish, hamster, ferret
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, scientist, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the scientist is the owner of the fish##1
3. the social-worker is the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the journalist and the owner of the fish##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Pet         | goldfish | fish      | hamster       | ferret    |
| Job           | librarian  | scientist  | social-worker | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

