.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, pop, hip-hop
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
8. the manager is on the left of the fan of pop##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | d&b  | pop     | hip-hop         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

