.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, monopoly, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, spy, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is between the german and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
4. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing scrabble is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game          | snooker | scrabble  | domino   | monopoly    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | spy     | superhero | disaster |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | russian | colombian | german   |

